features: HIGHT QUALITY BAMBOO SHELF UNIT - Keep clutter under control with this amazing tall storage shelf. Made of 100% natural bamboo material, durable and delicate. The surface of the shelf unit is coated with waterproof varnish, which can be used in the living room, study room, reading room, home office, bathroom, kitchen, and balcony. Our bookshelf can stand the test of time.

6-TIER ADJUSTABLE STANDING BOOKSHELF - Whether you decide to cascade your favorite house plants, show off your personal art gallery or collect your various books on this solid free-standing bookcase, its 6 adjustable shelves will support whatever you choose. Equipped with anti-tip fittings, the bookcase can be anchored to the wall so as to avoid wobbling or tipping.

SPACE SAVER SHELF FOR SMALL SPACES - 23.6"L * 10.2"W * 63.4"H, 6-tier book shelf of 10.2” deep perfect fit any room, creating more storage space for your home without taking up too much space. The height of each storage shelf can be adjusted according to your hobbies or the height of the items. This white bookshelf will bring a natural aesthetic style to your home.

MULTIPURPOSE STORAGE SHELF - Thick bamboo shelves with easy-to-tight screws can withstand heavy loads without being easily bent or deformed, each shelf can accommodate up to 33 lbs. Open wide design provides more space for storage, can be used as a bookcase, flower stand, kitchen shelf, bathroom rack for holding books, photo frames, plants, towels, baskets, and so on.

DURABLE BUT LIGHTWEIGHT - Structured with solid bamboo for extended durability, overall weight is 18.7 lbs. You can easily move the storage shelf and place it wherever you want. Perfectly spaced bars prevent the books from falling into the gap.

EASY ASSEMBLY - Tighten the shelves with screws as needed to complete the installation. Only 4 steps are required and no more than 10 minutes. Our easy-to-follow assembly instructions will guide you through each step. If the received item is defective, please feel free to contact Homykic customer support.
EASY TO MAINTENANCE - The surface of the bookshelf is smooth and moisture-proof, it is not easy to get dirty after long-time use. If stained, please wipe it with a damp cloth.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Solid design and attractive
reviews.reviewText: This bookshelf is perfect for my needs. It was easy to put together and you can adjust where each shelf is by screwing them into different pre-drilled spots.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Ridiculously Easy to Build and Perfect Width
reviews.reviewText: I ordered one of these for my hallway. I chose this one because the price was decent, the width (how far out from the wall it goes) was ideal, and they offered it in white.Turned out to be SUPER easy to put together. From unboxing to securing to the wall, less than one hour total (I did use an electric drill which helped speed things along).I ended up liking the first one so much I purchased a second one immediately and now they are side by side.They work great as shoe racks, but I'll be adding more than just shoes (as I'm not a shoe collector so don't have too many pair).If you're going to build one of these, my wee bits of advice are:1) Do pay attention to the fact that the screws go INTO the larger hole and EXIT the smaller hole.2) It's easier if you screw the lone bracing sticks (you'll know what I mean when you get the box) into one of the side panels BEFORE securing the second side panel. I didn't notice that step in the instructions, so I put both sides of the stand together with the shelves first... and had to add the bracing sticks afterward, but it really wasn't a big deal.3) I did have one split (see photos) so I just removed the screws from that shelf and turned it around so the split is in the rear of the stand. For $70 I don't expect perfection. The fact that all the holes are in the right place and all the parts were included is pretty much all I require.4) They do provide an extra of most of the metal parts, just in case. That's nice.5) I do believe this could be top-heavy and possibly dangerous so this is the first piece of furniture I've ever attached to a wall (the supplies for that are included). They're both quite sturdy now with no risk of falling.6) Although an allen wrench is included, I used my drill to put this together. Just saved so much time and didn't risk tennis elbow. You'll need a drill bit that has one of those star-shaped or hexagonal heads... luckily my kit had one. Yay!7) You can (within reason) choose the spacing on the shelves. I decided to make both of my stands the same with a taller opening at the bottom for my work boots.The only complaints I would have, and they're not big enough complaints to remove a star from my rating are:1) Weirdly the company doesn't include enough white sticker dots to cover all the screw holes. That seems weird. They include a small page of the stickers... why not include enough for both sides of the stand?2) The smell. But I'm used to this icky off-gassing smell from inexpensive furniture and hope it dissipates over time like the other ones. Again, you get what you pay for and I'm 100% satisfied with my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Coat closets CAN be a pantry instead!
reviews.reviewText: We transformed a coat closet off the kitchen into a useful pantry for our family of 6. This was taken just after the sheves were put into place. Now they are full of pots, pans, lunch items as well as small appliances and large items that aren't used everyday. It's been very useful and all at a very low cost. Shelves are sturdy and perfect for my use...but also attractive enough for a living space or more traditional use. A+
